                <h3 class="mt-4" id="op06">Invert text</h3>
                <p>This functionality inverts all text entered. It is worth mentioning that this property does not invert the text per line. It completely inverts, that is, with line breaks, the last letter of the entire text will become the first, and so on. To get the text back to normal, just click on the functionality again.</p>
