                <p>Below, as an example, we have in the figure 9 the inserted text: "Example. Manipulating text". In figure 10 we have the result of the transformation of the text after clicking on the "INVERT" button. Such a result is: "txet gnitalupinaM .elpmaxE".</p>
                
