                <h3 class="mt-4">1st letter per phrase</h3>
                <p>Called First Letter by Phrase, this functionality fulfills what is named when the set of words ends with a line break, period, exclamation point or question mark.</p>
                <h5 class="mt-4">Example:</h5>
                <p>In the example below, we have in figure 11, the text initially inserted: "example. manipulating text". In figure 12, as a result, after clicking on the option "1ST LETTER PER PHRASE", the text: "Example. Manipulating text". Therefore, it is easy to see that the transformation was made at the beginning of the text and after the period.</p>
                
