                <h3 class="mt-4">Word spacing</h3>
                <p>In this functionality, line breaks are replaced by space. That is, if the inserted text has line breaks, when applying this option, such line breaks will be removed, and a space will be added.</p>
                <h5 class="mt-4">Example:</h5>
                <p>In the example below we have in figure 13 the inserted text has a line break for each word of the phrase "Example. Manipulating text". In figure 14, the result is the same sentence, but without this line break.</p>

