                <h3 class="mt-4" id="op09">No empty line</h3>
                <p>In this functionality, there is the elimination of two or more line breaks in the inserted text, leaving only one line break. It is easy to see such utility by removing inaccurate amounts of line breaks. If you want to eliminate the remaining line, we advise you to take a look at the <a href="/options/page2/#op08" style="color: chocolate;">WORD SPACING functionality</a>.</p>
